<div style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 24px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;">
    <div style="max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px;">
            <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 16px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #0284c7 100%); color: #ffffff;">
                <span style="font-size: 22px;">💊</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h1 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; text-align: center; margin: 8px 0;">
            Votre ordonnance médicale
        </h1>

        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; margin-top: 12px;">
            Bonjour {{ patientName }},
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; margin-top: 8px;">
            Votre prescription du <strong>{{ dateOrdonnance }}</strong> est prête. Voici le récapitulatif de vos médicaments.
        </p>

        <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 16px; background-color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;">
            <p style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">Indications</p>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #334155; margin: 0;">{{ ordonnance.posologie }}</p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <p style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">Médicaments prescrits</p>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;">
                {% for med in medications %}
                <li style="padding: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px; background-color: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; color: #334155;">
                    <strong>{{ med.name }}</strong> – {{ med.dosage }} {{ med.forme }}<br>
                    <span style="font-size: 12px; color: #64748b;">{{ med.frequenceParJour }}x/jour • {{ med.nbJours }} jours • {{ med.momentPrise }}</span>
                </li>
                {% else %}
                <li style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">Aucun médicament spécifié.</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 24px; padding: 16px; background-color: #eff6ff; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
            <p style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #1e40af; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">Accès numérique – Scannez ou cliquez</p>
            {% if qrDataUri is defined and qrDataUri %}
            <img src="{{ qrDataUri }}" alt="QR Code prescription" style="width: 140px; height: 140px; display: block; margin: 0 auto 12px auto;" width="140" height="140">
            {% endif %}
            <a href="{{ scanUrl }}"
               style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #0ea5e9; color: #ffffff !important; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">
                Voir la prescription complète
            </a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 20px;">
            Si le bouton ne fonctionne pas, copiez ce lien dans votre navigateur :
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #0369a1; word-break: break-all; margin-top: 4px;">
            {{ scanUrl }}
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 20px;">
            À bientôt,<br>
            L'équipe médicale
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
